---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const description = "Free 85-page study analyzing 130 hackathons. Learn best practices, success factors, and insights from hackathon organizers and participants across Belgium.";
---

<Layout title="130 Hackathons Analyzed - Free Study" description={description} url="/130-hackathons-analyzed-for-you">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-12 text-gray-900">130 hackathons analyzed for you</h1>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/3 flex-shrink-0">
        <img 
          src="https://hackathon.be/wp-media/Hackathon-fake-book-cover.png" 
          alt="How to Organize Great Hackathons - Study Cover" 
          class="w-full max-w-sm mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          width="350" 
          height="350"
        />
      </div>
      
      <div class="md:w-2/3">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-800">
          How to Organize Great Hackathons
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Get the study based on data from hackathons in Belgium:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center text-lg">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">✓</span>
            <span><strong class="font-semibold">130 events</strong> analyzed</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-lg">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">✓</span>
            <span><strong class="font-semibold">50 examples</strong> included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-lg">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">✓</span>
            <span><strong class="font-semibold">13 testimonials</strong> from experts</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-lg">
            <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3">✓</span>
            <span><strong class="font-semibold">85 pages</strong> of insights</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-lg">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          More than 150 public hackathons have been organized in Belgium since 2011. 
          <a href="http://www.convidencia.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-semibold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Convidencia</a>, 
          experts in hackathons, analysed events based on data and experience from 130 events. 
          <strong class="text-blue-700">They published their study for FREE!</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What you get</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
        In 85 pages, you get practical tips to help you concretely set up a hackathon:
      </p>
      
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Best time in the year to organize your event</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Roles of the different organizers</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Top 5 business models</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Clear objectives for the event (a hackathon about what, for whom, how long, etc.) whether for organizers or participants</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Ideal locations</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Key details for a great event (good wifi, catering, showers, etc.)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Advice to find a name for your event</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-600 mr-3 mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Top 10 common mistakes to avoid</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Download</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Get the results after months of research, investigation and analysis, and find all the information 
        about these events gathered in this unique study:
      </p>

      <div class="text-center my-12">
        <a 
          href="http://bit.ly/StudyPublicHackathons" 
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold text-lg px-12 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105"
        >
          Get the Study FREE
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          <strong>Published:</strong> December 27, 2017 | 
          <strong>Tags:</strong> 
          <span class="inline-flex gap-2 ml-2">
            <span class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs">download</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs">free</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs">hackathon</span>
            <span class="bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs">study</span>
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
